releaseNotes:
• Added a 'Skip This Version' button in the software update dialog (issue #437).
  • Removed the default list of sensitive applications (issue #466).
  • A replacement choice is now offered when moving the combo list file (issue #467).
  • Added a thank-you message for translators in the About dialog (issue #483).
  • Fixed the background of the picker window when custom theme is off (issue #492).
  • Fixed the tab order in the combo dialog (issue #57).
  • Restored the ability to re-use keywords (issue #482).
